sentence: i need a one way flight from <*tacoma*> <to> !tacoma to san jose leaving in the morning before seven a m
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  v0.departure_time, '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v5.flight_id||'"', '"'||v6.fare_id||'"', '"'||v6.round_trip_required||'"' FROM flight v0,
 airport_service v1,
 city v2, airport_service v3, city v4, flight_fare v5, fare v6 
WHERE ((v0.departure_time BETWEEN  0 AND  1200) AND (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) 
AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) 
AND (v2.city_name = 'TACOMA'))) AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) 
AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'SAN JOSE'))) AND ((v0.departure_time <  700) 
AND ((v0.flight_id = ANY v5.flight_id) AND ((v5.fare_id = ANY v6.fare_id) 
AND ((v6.round_trip_required = 'NO') 
AND ( 1 =  1))))))));
